data.description: Sango welcomes you with the epitome of luxury living, offering an in-ground pool, with outdoor bluetooth speakers and store your pool gear in convenient bins. Unwind in the outdoor shower or the matching pool house, w/ it's own HVAC. Best of all, this home is situated on almost an acre of land with no HOA! Inside, you'll be greeted by stunning accent walls, gorgeous ceilings, chic light fixtures, new LVP flooring, plush carpets, tile and gleaming hardwood throughout. Five deluxe bedrooms, in which two offer their very own bathroom, with the largest primary suite located on the main level. The kitchen offers brand new appliances and there's a sleek bar in the Florida room (with a mini-fridge that’s yours to keep!). A bonus room, office, and spacious nooks offer endless possibilities! And don't forget the cozy living room fireplace, fenced-in dog run, and laundry room that leads to the garage. The pool has closed for the season, Seller is offering to pay for the opening at Spring season!
